<div align="center"><strong> Volunteer Opportunities</strong></div>
<p>We offer a wide range of programming, both within our house and through our many community connections. From after-school programs, English classes and environmental initiatives to volunteer work with people living with disabilities, we are sure that there is a program fit for you.<br />
<br style="clear: both;"><a title="Volunteer Positions" href="volunteer-positions/">read more..</a></p>
